snippet.title: Mon Boleche Amar | Love Express | Dev | Nusrat Jahan | Jeet Gannguli | Rajib Kumar | 2016

localized.description:
Fall in love with the most adored love song 'Mon Boleche Amar' from Love Express, starring Dev and Nusrat. This romantic number has been composed and rendered by Jeet Gannguli. 

Film : Love Express
Starring : Dev, Nusrat Jahan & Others
Presenter : Shrikant Mohta & Nispal Singh
Produced by : Shree Venkatesh Films & Surinder Films
Direction: Rajib Kumar
Screenplay & Dialogue : N.K. Salil
D.O.P : Sailesh Avasthi
Music : Jeet Gannguli
Singer : Jeet Gannguli
Rap: Bob & Prasen
Lyrics: Prasen
Edit : Md.Kalam
Choreographer : Arvind Thakur
---------------------------------------------------------------------------
